These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-7-1::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, cranberry, cabbage
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, coffee
House: tower, colonial, cottage
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, tulip, marigold
1. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the cottage house##5
2. the tower house is in the middle##1
3. the tower house is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
4. the person who growstulip is between the colonial house and the person drinking coffee##2
5. the person drinking milk is not the person eating artichoke##6
6. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the person eating artichoke and the person eating cabbage##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |    3     |
| Food         | cabbage | cranberry | artichoke  |
| Beverage   | milk     | fanta     | coffee |
| House         | colonial     | tower   | cottage  |
| Flower     | poppy        | tulip   | marigold      |

