.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-7-2::.
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, american, polish
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, tulip, lily
There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, turquise, mauve
City: miami, hannover, liverpool
1. the person who growstulip is the colombian##1
2. the polish is on the right of the american##1
3. the polish is the person who likes mauve##1
4. the person who likes lilac is somewhere between the person traveling to hannover and the person traveling to liverpool##7
5. the polish is somewhere to the right of the colombian##5
6. the person who growslily is in the middle##1
7. the person who likes turquise is the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |    3    |
| Nationality   | colombian  | american   | polish |
| Flower   | tulip | lily    | zinnia    |
| Color           | turquise  | lilac       | mauve |
| City         | hannover    | miami | liverpool  |

