.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-7-3::.
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, thai, canadian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, skiing, swimming
City: hamburg, colone, edinburgh
House: victorian, colonial, art-deco
1. the person who's sport is skiing is the art-deco house##1
2. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the left of the victorian house##5
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is not the person who's sport is swimming##6
5. the victorian house is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
6. the canadian is between the person who's sport is swimming and the thai##2
7. the canadian is somewhere between the person traveling to hamburg and the person who's sport is skiing##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |
| Nationality      | nigerian           | canadian  | thai |
| Sport         | swimming | snowboarding   | skiing  |
| City           | hamburg       | edinburgh   | colone   |
| House   | colonial        | victorian | art-deco     |

