.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-7-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, brazilian, russian
House: modern, farmhouse, tower
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, satire, comedy
3 different pets are kept: lizard, guinea-pig, frog
1. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
2. the modern house is somewhere to the right of the tower house##5
3. the modern house is the person watching epic movies##1
4. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
5. the modern house is on the left or right of the russian##3
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere between the person watching satire movies and the tower house##7
7. the russian is somewhere to the left of the person watching epic movies##5
8. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3       |
| Nationality      | russian       | indonesian     | brazilian         |
| House         | tower | modern    | farmhouse      |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy       | epic | satire       |
| Pet         | frog  | guinea-pig    | lizard |

