3. the owner of the hedgehog is not the person driving the taxi##6
4. the townhouse house is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
5. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
6. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
7. the person driving the van is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |    3     |
