City: hamburg, venice, edinburgh
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike, train
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, photography, singing
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is photography##5
3. the person drinking juice is the person driving the quad-bike##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere between the person traveling to hamburg and the person driving the train##7
6. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's hobby is photography##1
7. the person traveling to venice is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hamburg##5
8. the person driving the motorbike is not the person drinking juice##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |
| Beverage           | juice | water | iced-tea |
| City   | hamburg    | edinburgh         | venice    |
| Transport           | quad-bike  | motorbike        | train       |
| Hobby         | board-games | singing     | photography  |

