2. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
3. the fan pop is on the far right##1
4. the fan soul is not the person eating cauliflower##6
5. the person driving the taxi is somewhere between the person eating peach and the person driving the motorbike##7
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3      |
| Food         | peach | cauliflower      | avocado    |
| Transport           | jet-ski | taxi | motorbike  |
| Color   | red   | ebony       | lilac    |
| Music-Genre   | soul   | techno       | pop |

