3. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere between the person drinking fanta and the vegafina-smoker##7
4. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person eating radish##1
5. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person eating radish##1
6. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the davidoff-smoker##5

