The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, police-officer, mechanic
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, rugby, cricket
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: time-travel, satire, family
1. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
2. the security-guard is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
3. the security-guard is somewhere to the right of the person who likes turquise##5
4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
6. the security-guard is somewhere between the mechanic and the person who's sport is cricket##7
7. the mechanic is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
8. the person who likes turquise is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Color      | turquise     | ivory | lilac |
| Job          | police-officer | security-guard   | mechanic      |
| Sport   | cricket    | rugby        | handball       |
| Movie-Genre   | family  | time-travel      | satire     |

