3. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is not the person who growsorchid##6
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker##3
6. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the dunhill-smoker##7
7. the blend-smoker is the blend-smoker##1
8. the person drinking sprite is not the person who growsdahlia##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |        2        |     3      |
| Cigar        | dunhill        | blend      | bongani    |
| City         | marseilles | edinburgh | venice   |
| Beverage       | sprite  | almond-milk   | coffee |
