3. the fan indie is not the person who's birthday is in february##6
4. the fan r&b is somewhere to the left of the person playing domino##5
5. the person who's birthday is in december is in the middle##1
6. the fan dubstep is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in june and the owner of the dog##7
7. the owner of the hamster is in the middle##1
8. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |      3      |
| Birthday          | february   | december  | june |
| Pet   | dog  | hamster    | bird     |
| Music-Genre         | r&b    | dubstep   | indie       |
