.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-7-20::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, bellflower, poppy
3 different games are played: scrabble, bridge, snooker
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, vegafina, dunhill
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, writing, sudoku
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the left of the person who growsrose##5
3. the person playing snooker is somewhere between the person playing scrabble and the vegafina-smoker##7
4. the dunhill-smoker is somewhere between the alhambra-smoker and the vegafina-smoker##7
5. the person who growsbellflower is the alhambra-smoker##1
6. the person who growspoppy is somewhere between the person playing bridge and the person who's hobby is photography##7

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |      3       |
| Flower   | bellflower | poppy      | rose       |
| Game        | scrabble | snooker         | bridge |
| Cigar        | alhambra     | dunhill        | vegafina         |
| Hobby      | photography  | sudoku | writing      |

 